What you need to know:  The only Champions League final Ancelotti has lost as a coach came 17 years ago when his AC Milan side blew a 3-0 half-time lead before losing to Liverpool on penalties.Ancelotti had already made history this season by becoming the first manager to win all the titles in Europe's top five leagues by adding La Liga to his Serie A, Premier League, Ligue 1 and Bundesliga championships with AC Milan, Chelsea, PSG and Bayern respectively.